channel.title: Do you mind
channel.description:
Well, Again, Recently i have put a topic on what should i post for a tutorial, Cause i have nothing to do, And without my job for 1 more week, I have alot of spare time on my hands, And people liked my idea of posting a tutorial on how to get a Command Generator on some batch files, So the thing is
[b]Do you care if i post a topic on how to get command generators on batch files[/b]
If you do, Tell me the reason, Weather you think its going to be copy and paste, People should find out for them selves and so forth.
If you don't mind, Tell me if there is anything i shouldn't post, Copy and paste-able scripts, So forth.
So if you could post a reply, Thanks, I really need it.
